General.Name: Eclatorq Technology Co. Ltd.
General.Description: Eclatorq Technology Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells hand tools in Taiwan. It offers digital torque wrenches, digital angle torque wrenches, digital adjustable spanners, digital mini torque wrenches, digital screwdrivers, digital adaptors, wireless digital torque wrenches, wireless digital angle torque wrenches, digital torque testers, calibration equipment, and adaptors. Eclatorq Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 2006 is based in Taichung, Taiwan.
